## Critical Snippets

### tenantFilter (Repository — ใช้ทุก Query)
```javascript
function tenantFilter(userContext) {
  return {
    ou_id:      new ObjectId(userContext.ou_id),
    branch_id:  new ObjectId(userContext.branch_id),
    is_deleted: false,
  };
}
```

### Audit Fields — CREATE (ตั้ง cr_* + upd_* พร้อมกัน)
```javascript
const now = new Date();
const payload = {
  ...data,
  ...tenantFilter(userContext),
  cr_by:    userContext.username,
  cr_date:  now,
  cr_prog:  '/api/v1/<resource>',
  upd_by:   userContext.username,  // ← ต้อง set ด้วย
  upd_date: now,
  upd_prog: '/api/v1/<resource>',
};
```

### Audit Fields — UPDATE (upd_* เท่านั้น)
```javascript
const setPayload = {
  ...updateData,
  upd_by:   userContext.username,
  upd_date: new Date(),
  upd_prog: '/api/v1/<resource>',
};
```

### Optimistic Locking check
```javascript
const filter = { _id: new ObjectId(id), ...tenantFilter(userContext), upd_date: original_upd_date };
const oldDoc = await db.collection('...').findOne(filter, { session });
if (!oldDoc) throw new AppError(409, 'CONFLICT', 'Data not found or already modified');
```

### Soft Delete payload
```javascript
{
  is_deleted:   true,
  deleted_by:   userContext.username,
  deleted_date: now,
  deleted_prog: '/api/v1/<resource>',
  upd_by:       userContext.username,
  upd_date:     now,
  upd_prog:     '/api/v1/<resource>',
}
```

### Transaction Shell
```javascript
const client = getClient();
const session = client.startSession();
try {
  let result;
  await session.withTransaction(async () => {
    const db = getDatabase();
    const now = new Date();
    // 1. Main write operation
    // 2. Insert log (same session)
    result = ...;
  });
  return result;
} finally {
  await session.endSession();
}
```

### Log Document
```javascript
await db.collection('<resource>_logs').insertOne({
  ref_id:     docId,
  ou_id:      new ObjectId(userContext.ou_id),
  branch_id:  new ObjectId(userContext.branch_id),
  action:     'INSERT' | 'UPDATE' | 'DELETE',
  changed_fields: null | { field: { old: oldVal, new: newVal } },
  snapshot_data:  { old: null | oldDoc, new: payload | null },
  cr_by:      userContext.username,
  cr_date:    now,
  cr_prog:    '/api/v1/<resource>',
}, { session });
```

### serializeDoc (แปลง Decimal128 + Date ก่อนส่ง response)
```javascript
import { serializeDoc } from '../../utils/format.js';

// LIST
data.map((d) => ({ id: d._id.toString(), ...serializeDoc(d) }))

// DETAIL
doc ? { id: doc._id.toString(), ...serializeDoc(doc) } : null

// เก็บค่าเงินลง DB
price: Decimal128.fromString(String(data.price))
```

### AppError
```javascript
throw new AppError(400, 'INVALID_PARAM', 'message');
throw new AppError(409, 'CONFLICT', 'Code already exists');
throw new AppError(401, 'UNAUTHORIZED', 'Invalid token');
```

### Duplicate Key (2-layer guard)
```javascript
const existing = await col.findOne({ ou_id, branch_id, code }, { session });
if (existing) throw new AppError(409, 'CONFLICT', 'Code already exists');
try {
  await col.insertOne(payload, { session });
} catch (err) {
  if (err.code === 11000) throw new AppError(409, 'CONFLICT', 'Code already exists');
  throw err;
}
```

### Response
```javascript
// Success list
res.status(200).json({ success: true, code: 'SUCCESS', message: null, data: [...], pagination: { page, limit, total, totalPages } });

// Success single
res.status(200).json({ success: true, code: 'SUCCESS', message: null, data: { ... } });

// Not found
res.status(200).json({ success: true, code: 'DATA_NOT_FOUND', message: null, data: null });

// Error — ห้าม res.json() เอง
} catch (err) { next(err); }
```
